Preheat oven to 350 degrees (325 degrees for nonstick #baking sheet{}).

Grease a #baking sheet{}. Place @Annie's Organic Cinnamon Rolls{1%24 ounce} 2 inches apart on prepared sheet.

Bake until golden brown, ~{18-20%minutes}. Remove from sheet and let cool slightly.

Cut tip from corner of @icing pouch{1}(cut tip from corner), squeeze icing over cinnamon rolls, and serve.

> Nutritions per 1 roll: 320 kcal, 11g fat, 4.5g saturated fat, 53g carbohydrates, 24g sugar, 4g protein, 2g fiber, 760mg sodium.